org.sql: SELECT DISTINCT users.* FROM users LEFT OUTER JOIN members ON users.id = members.user_id AND members.project_id = 21 LEFT OUTER JOIN member_roles ON members.id = member_roles.member_id LEFT OUTER JOIN roles ON users.type = 'User' AND (roles.id = member_roles.role_id OR member_roles.role_id IS NULL AND roles.builtin = 1) OR users.type = 'AnonymousUser' AND roles.builtin = 2 LEFT OUTER JOIN role_permissions ON roles.id = role_permissions.role_id AND role_permissions.permission = 'view_work_packages' WHERE users.type IN ("$1", "$2", "$3") AND (roles.id IS NOT NULL AND role_permissions.id IS NOT NULL OR users.admin = True)
